Each of my multiple visits had very little wait time, which is important to me.
I highly recommend Dr Schreiber to everyone.
He is fast, thorough, and very serious about his profession.
So his office is a little old.
No big deal.
I would rather have a good Doctor who takes care of business, rather than one who cares more about the drapes in the waiting room.
As far as I am concerned, "He is the man"

